I would say the benefits that I have gained from HKU SPACE CC are maturity and critical thinking. In Media and Cultural Studies, I have come across the relevant ideologies and concepts, and all these have made me become more sensitive to our surrounding world. Personality wise, I turned out to be very determined on striving for goals, since the keen competition at CC can get pretty fierce and tough sometimes. All these as highlighted above are actually priceless skills and mindsets that I have gained throughout my previous Associate Degree’s level studies.






Chow Ka Yi Cissy

